&lt;Hyundai Auto Canada Inc>, a unit ofSouth Korea's Hyundai Motor Co &lt;HYUN.SE>, is expected to awardChemical Asia Ltd a mandate later this week to arrange a 100mln U.S. Dlr loan, banking sources said.    The nine-year loan will carry interest of 1/4 point overthe London interbank offered rate. No other details wereavailable.    A Chemical spokesman declined comment. REUTER&#3;